.Dd June 2, 1993
.Dt CREAT 2
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm creat
.Nd create a new file
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In fcntl.h
.Ft int
.Fn creat "const char *path" "mode_t mode"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Bf -symbolic
This interface is made obsolete by:
.Ef
.Xr open 2 .
.Pp
The
.Fn creat
function
is the same as:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
open(path, O_CREAT | O_TRUNC | O_WRONLY, mode);
.Ed
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr open 2
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Fn creat
function appeared in
.At v6 .
